Package studyprogress

Class Summary
Course Course is the class containing the key data describing a single university course.
CustomCourseListener Button listener class for graphical custom Course creation screen.
CustomModuleListener Button listener class for graphical custom Module creation screen.
LoginButtonListener Button listener class for graphical login screen.
Main Main class.
MainButtonListener Button listener class for graphical main menu screen.
ModelCourseListener Button listener class for the graphical model Course creation screen.
ModelModuleListener Button listener class for the graphical model Module creation screen.
Module Module is the class containing the key data describing an university study module, such as Basic Studies in Computer Science.
ModuleListListener List listener class for graphical main menu's Module and Course lists.
Semester Semester is a class containing the credit point total and number of Courses finished during a specified Semester.
SemesterTableModel Custom table model class for the Semester data table in the graphical main menu screen.
Student Student is the class representing an university student, the user of this software.
StudyCLI The command line interface-class fort StudyProgressManager.
StudyGUI The Graphical User Interface-class for StudyProgressManager
StudyProgressManager StudyProgressManager is the class containing the basic operations of the StudyProgress-application, such as logging in and creating a user.
